{"tid":1208303,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[未出得去嘅幫幫手] 白宮聯署 緊急發案制裁香港政府","createTime":"2019-06-12T09:15:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T10:32:47.000Z","uid":28159,"like":41,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"834cd5bbc28469690051cf83ee5e6062bc243c85","tid":1208303,"uid":28159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T09:15:07.000Z","msg":"麻煩各位幫手draft一draft個聯署, 要求國會討論通過緊急法案, 禁止美國公司對香港政府輸出軍需物品，包括電子零件，通訊，導航設備及武器<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Sanctioning Hong Kong Government on Their Use of Deadly Force against Un-armed Citizens</span><br />\n<br />\nOn 12 Jun, the Hong Kong Police Force have widely used deadly force towards unarmed protesters who surround the Council and Central Government Offices.<br />\n<br />\nTo show the world that the States widely support the free world, we urge Congress to pass an Emergency Act for sanctioning Hong Kong Government. The United States, under the bill, stop supplying any Strategic Commodities including but not limited to computer chips, navigation and avionics instrument or weapons."},{"pid":"be7531414382560d560c3579d0fb49045c6637cf","tid":1208303,"uid":139677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T09:15:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"27967709677b57be2a0e48f6a9ffc30361b75b90","tid":1208303,"uid":143827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T09:16:34.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"80bc141927b40dcfcc0e28971f0e5a26376ca4f2","tid":1208303,"uid":48531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T09:16:35.000Z","msg":"冇link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b37ab609168e880a779fa213d80f7fa14ca3cdb4","tid":1208303,"uid":28159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80bc141927b40dcfcc0e28971f0e5a26376ca4f2","tid":1208303,"uid":48531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T09:16:35.000Z","msg":"冇link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wond